-- TIGHT FORMS: prefix, tight infix, juxtaposition

-- Prefix forms
=== prefix negative | 80
-x

=== prefix colon | 80
:foo

=== prefix tilde | 80
~[1 2 3]

-- Tight infix forms
=== dot notation | 80
x.y

=== dot chain | 80
a.b.c.d

=== tight colon | 80
foo:bar

-- Juxtaposition
=== function call | 80
f(x)

=== chained calls | 80
f(x)(y)

=== indexing | 80
f(x)[i]

=== complex juxt | 80
foo(bar)[baz](qux)
